kind: PeerAuthentication
metadata:
  name: default
  namespace: production
spec:
  mtls:
    mode: STRICT  # REJECT plain-text connections between services
```

**What this gives you for free**: Every call from order-service to payment-service is now encrypted and mutually authenticated — no code changes needed. Istio handles certificate rotation automatically.

