**Rollout schedule:**
```text
Day 1:  10% → monitor error rates and latency for 24h
Day 2:  25% → check conversion rate vs control group
Day 3:  50% → final verification
Day 4: 100% → full rollout, remove flag from code in next sprint

If problems at any stage:
  PUT /api/admin/features/new-checkout-flow {"enabled": false}
  → 0ms rollback, no deployment needed, 0 users see new flow
```

