## Monitor the rollout

```java
// Track feature usage with Micrometer
public CheckoutResult processCheckout(CheckoutRequest request, Long userId) {
    boolean useNew = unleash.isEnabled("new-checkout-flow", context);
    String variant = useNew ? "new" : "old";

    Timer.Sample sample = Timer.start();
    try {
        CheckoutResult result = useNew
            ? newCheckout.process(request)
            : oldCheckout.process(request);

        sample.stop(Timer.builder("checkout.duration")
            .tag("variant", variant)
            .register(meterRegistry));

        checkoutSuccessCounter.increment(variant);
        return result;

    } catch (Exception e) {
        checkoutErrorCounter.increment(variant);
        throw e;
    }
}
```

**Grafana query to compare variants:**
```text
# New checkout error rate vs old:
rate(checkout_errors_total{variant="new"}[5m]) /
rate(checkout_total{variant="new"}[5m])

# If new-checkout error rate > 2x old-checkout error rate → roll back!
```

